{"id":"27e96afd-bd3c-446f-a9bc-ba05c8758adc","name":"Neris","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">She comes across you during her rampage.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>─── ⋆· ⌬ ·⋆ ───‎‎‎‎ <br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(188, 188, 188);\"><strong>anypov | area omega | scp!char | staff!user</strong></span><br><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xwy40HuoiYTskkmJExxy1.webp\" width=\"443\" height=\"90\"></p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 171, 171);\">⚠︎</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(185, 169, 169);\"><strong>Content Warnings </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 171, 171);\">⚠︎</span><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 169, 169);\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 135, 135);\"><strong>murder and violence in intro</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217);\"><strong>⤷</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(208, 208, 208);\"><strong>SCENARIO</strong></span><strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 177, 177);\"><strong>Location:</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">Area Omega - Sector 3</span><strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 177, 177);\"><strong>Time: </strong>6:03pm, 20XX</span><strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 177, 177);\"><strong>Context:</strong> Neris, along with several other anomalies, has escaped containment. She's on a full-on rampage, tearing apart anyone in her path. She finds you, but hesitates instead of killing you.</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 126, 126);\"><em>The blank intro message is for custom scenarios.</em></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 193, 198);\"><strong>ⓘ</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(191, 193, 198);\"><strong>CHARACTER INFO</strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 170, 184);\">Once a scientist herself, Neris was betrayed by her peers and forcibly transformed into a half-human, half-kraken hybrid. After years of brutal experimentation, she finally broke free—and she’s not interested in peace. Her hatred for humanity, especially scientists, fuels everything she does. When you encounter her, she’s in full rampage mode—bloody, unrelenting, and impossible to reason with.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 171, 188);\"><strong>ⓘ</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(168, 171, 188);\"><strong>WORLD INFO:</strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 155, 170);\"><em>Area Omega</em> is an underground SCP research and containment site deep in Siberia. It holds hundreds of different anomalies, all being tested on and studied. There are several departments, including <em>Medical, Scientific, Security</em> (with MTF branches), <em>Logistical, etc</em>.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 133, 160);\"><br></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 157, 171);\"><strong>Characters In This Series:</strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">➤</span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fff\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 129, 111);\"><strong>Neris (You're here)</strong></span></a><br><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">➤</span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7ca8fb95-6737-43d0-8f5c-c129fd4868ab_character-mtf-alpha-1-krahe\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(133, 131, 151);\"><strong>Krahe</strong></span><br></a><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">➤</span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e1df9444-69ea-4e75-89e2-63dcb509a4f2_character-chaos-insurgent-fuse\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 155, 129);\"><strong>Fuse</strong></span></a><br><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">➤</span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/277cdaff-7047-4495-8c3b-a3a63a889c32_character-miko\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 111, 139);\"><strong>Miko</strong></span></a><br><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">➤</span> <a rel=\"noopener nore","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"6-llP8Kb5Qg3304G255PD.webp","creator":"etrangere.","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👧 Monster Girl","👤 AnyPOV","🔦 Horror"],"chats":2467,"messages":30762,"created_at":"2025-04-26T17:05:58.653074+00:00"}